trans-unit.source: Represents an item in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et element i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A RepeaterItem object represents an item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control, such as the heading section, footer section, or a data item.
trans-unit.target: Et RepeaterItem-objekt som representerer et element i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontroll, for eksempel delen overskrift, bunnteksten eller et dataelement.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>

trans-unit.source: The data items of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control are stored in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection> object that can be accessed by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control.
trans-unit.target: Dataelementer for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontrollen er lagret i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>objektet kan nås ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>

trans-unit.source: You can use a RepeaterItem object to programmatically access the properties of an item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke en RepeaterItem objektet programmatisk tilgang egenskaper for et element i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette og starte en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>

trans-unit.source: The index of the item in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"></xref> control from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items*> collection of the control.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for elementet i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"> </xref> kontrollere fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items*>samlingen kontrollens.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items*>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemType"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemType"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a data item associated with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et dataelement som er knyttet til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"> </xref> objekt i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Use the DataItem property to specify or determine the properties of a data item associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> object in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control.
trans-unit.target: Bruk DataItem-egenskapen til å angi eller finne ut hvilke egenskaper på et dataelement som er knyttet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>objekt i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This property only applies to data items in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne egenskapen gjelder bare for elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem.ItemType%2A> property must be set to `ListItemType.Item`, `ListItemType.AlternatingItem`, `ListItemType.SelectedItem`, or `ListItemType.EditItem`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem.ItemType%2A>egenskapen må være satt til `ListItemType.Item`, `ListItemType.AlternatingItem`, `ListItemType.SelectedItem`, eller `ListItemType.EditItem`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem.ItemType%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Object?displayProperty=fullName> that represents a data item in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object?displayProperty=fullName> som representerer et dataelement i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Use the ItemIndex property to determine the index number of the item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items%2A> collection of the control.
trans-unit.target: Bruk ItemIndex-egenskapen for å finne ut hvor indeksen for elementet i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontrollere fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items%2A>samlingen kontrollens.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This property only applies to data items in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne egenskapen gjelder bare for elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem.ItemType%2A> property must be set to `ListItemType.Item`, `ListItemType.AlternatingItem`, `ListItemType.SelectedItem`, or `ListItemType.EditItem`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem.ItemType%2A>egenskapen må være satt til `ListItemType.Item`, `ListItemType.AlternatingItem`, `ListItemType.SelectedItem`, eller `ListItemType.EditItem`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem.ItemType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The index of the item in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"></xref> control from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items*> collection of the control.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for elementet i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"> </xref> kontrollere fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items*>samlingen kontrollens.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.Items*>

trans-unit.target: Henter typen for elementet i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Use the ItemType property to determine the type of an item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control.
trans-unit.target: Bruk ItemType-egenskapen for å finne ut hva slags et element i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>
